   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 100 Families in Mexico to Start Saving</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our programs serve to reduce poverty in rural and marginalized communities in Baja California Sur, Mexico. Through personalized training, we accompany community members to create a self-managed Community Savings Group (CSG) that offers them the opportunity to save and have access to loans (generated from their own fund), with the aim of improving the families&apos; quality of life. We include dynamic financial education workshops that support participants to improve their family financial status.</narrative>
  </description>
